<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Yuragim Senga ҲСХМ130</title>
<lyrics>[C1]
.     D                F#m
   //  Yuragim Senga quloq tutar,
.  G                  D      A
   Koʻzlarim Senga, boqib tutar!
.  D                F#m  Bm
   Sen, bilan dilim quvonar,
.  G       A         D
   Hayotimning Egasisang! //

[V1]
.D            G            Asus4 A
 Minnotdarmiz Sening, muhabbatingga!
.D             G              Asus4  A
 Cheksiz shafqating uchun, rahmat Senga!
.Bm             G
 Sen Hudoyimiz, Otojonimiz,
.D                Asus4 A
 Doim panohing bizda.
.D            G            Asus4   A
 Minnotdarmiz Sen bizlarni tanlading!
.D           G          Asus4   A
 Yurakni poklading, Masihiy qilding,
.Bm            G
 Sen umidimiz, kuch-qudratimiz,
.D                Asus4 A
 Sening irodang bizda!__</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<author>Nodira Xoshimova</author>
<hymn_number>130</hymn_number>
</song>